### MomsTalk API — VS Code REST Client 실기기 테스트
### 사용법: VS Code에 "REST Client" 확장 설치 후 각 요청 위 "Send Request" 클릭
###
### 실행 순서:
###   1. 서버 기동: uvicorn app.main:app --reload  (backend/ 디렉터리에서)
###   2. 이 파일을 VS Code에서 열기
###   3. Step 1부터 순서대로 "Send Request" 클릭
###   4. 응답에서 토큰/ID를 복사해 아래 변수(@token 등)에 붙여넣기

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### [변수] 각 단계 실행 후 응답값을 여기에 붙여넣으세요
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Step 2 응답의 access_token
@lurkerToken = PASTE_LURKER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

# Step 3 응답의 access_token
@memberToken = PASTE_MEMBER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

# Step 4 응답의 access_token (refresh 후)
@newAccessToken = PASTE_NEW_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

# Step 6 응답의 id
@postId = PASTE_POST_ID_HERE

# Step 13 응답의 id
@commentId = PASTE_COMMENT_ID_HERE

# Step 15 응답의 id
@convId = PASTE_CONV_ID_HERE

# Step 14 응답의 id (두 번째 유저)
@user2Id = PASTE_USER2_ID_HERE

# Step 16 응답의 token
@inviteToken = PASTE_INVITE_TOKEN_HERE

# Step 19 응답의 id
@captureId = PASTE_CAPTURE_ID_HERE

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 0 ── 서버 헬스체크
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 1 ── 학교 검색 (NEIS API)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name searchSchool
GET {{baseUrl}}/schools/search?q=서울초등학교

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 2 ── [개발 전용] lurker 로그인
###           → 응답의 access_token을 @lurkerToken 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name lurkerLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/dev/lurker-login

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 3 ── [개발 전용] 정회원 로그인 (SMS 인증 없이)
###           → 응답의 access_token을 @memberToken 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name devLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/dev/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "01011112222",
  "region": "서울",
  "school_code": "B100000393",
  "school_name": "테스트초등학교",
  "grade": 2,
  "school_type": "elementary"
}

###

### ─── Step 3-1 ── lurker → 정회원 승급 (Step 3 토큰 필요) ───

# @name approveMe
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/dev/approve-me
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 4 ── Refresh 토큰으로 새 Access 토큰 발급
###           (Step 3 응답의 refresh_token 사용)
###           → 응답의 access_token을 @newAccessToken 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name refreshToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_FROM_STEP3_HERE"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 5 ── 내 프로필 조회
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name getMe
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ─── Step 5-1 ── 닉네임 변경 ───

# @name updateNickname
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/me/nickname
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "따뜻한엄마1234"
}

###

### ─── Step 5-2 ── 프로필(학교/학년) 변경 ───

# @name updateProfile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/auth/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "region": "경기",
  "school_code": "J100000001",
  "school_name": "새학교초등학교",
  "grade": 3,
  "school_type": "elementary"
}

###

### ─── Step 5-3 ── FCM 토큰 등록 ───

# @name registerFcmToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/me/fcm-token
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "fcm-device-token-example-12345"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 6 ── 게시글 작성
###           → 응답의 id를 @postId 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name createPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "안녕하세요, 2학년 학부모입니다",
  "content": "오늘 학교에서 있었던 일을 공유하고 싶어서 글을 올립니다. 아이가 즐겁게 학교생활을 하고 있어요.",
  "board_type": "free",
  "is_anonymous": true
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 7 ── 게시판별 게시글 목록 조회
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name listPosts_free
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?board_type=free&page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name listPosts_school
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?board_type=school
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name listPosts_grade
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?board_type=grade
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name searchPosts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?board_type=free&q=학부모
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 8 ── 게시글 단건 조회 (Step 6의 postId 필요)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name getPost
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 9 ── 게시글 수정
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name updatePost
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "수정된 제목입니다",
  "content": "내용을 수정했습니다. 더 자세한 내용을 추가했어요."
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 10 ── 좋아요 토글 (한 번 더 누르면 취소)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name likePost
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 11 ── 스크랩 토글
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name scrapPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/scrap
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name myScrapList
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/me/scraps
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 12 ── 신고
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name reportPost
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/report
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target_type": "post",
  "target_id": {{postId}},
  "category": "SPAM",
  "reason": "광고성 게시글입니다"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 13 ── 댓글 작성
###            → 응답의 id를 @commentId 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name createComment
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "좋은 글 감사합니다!",
  "is_anonymous": true
}

###

# @name createReply
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "저도 같은 경험이 있어요",
  "parent_id": {{commentId}},
  "is_anonymous": true
}

###

# @name listComments
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name likeComment
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments/{{commentId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name deleteComment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 14 ── 두 번째 유저 생성 (DM 테스트용)
###             → 응답의 access_token으로 /auth/me 호출 후
###               응답의 id를 @user2Id 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name devLogin2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/dev/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "01099998888",
  "region": "부산",
  "school_code": "D100000001",
  "school_name": "부산테스트초등학교",
  "grade": 3,
  "school_type": "elementary"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 15 ── DM 대화방 생성/조회
###             → 응답의 id를 @convId 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name startConversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{user2Id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name listConversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name sendMessage
POST {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{convId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "안녕하세요! 저도 같은 학교 학부모예요."
}

###

# @name listMessages
GET {{baseUrl}}/conversations/{{convId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ─── 차단/해제 ───

# @name blockUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{user2Id}}/block
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name unblockUser
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{user2Id}}/block
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 16 ── 초대 링크 발급 (정회원만 가능)
###             → 응답의 token을 @inviteToken 에 붙여넣기
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name generateInvite
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/invite/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# @name checkInvite
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/invite/{{inviteToken}}

###

# @name useInvite (lurker 계정으로 사용)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/invite/use
Authorization: Bearer {{lurkerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{inviteToken}}",
  "grade": 2,
  "class_num": 3
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 17 ── SMS 인증 플로우 (실제 SMS 없이 토큰만 확인)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name sendSms
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/sms/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "01012345678"
}

###

# @name verifySms  (개발 모드: 콘솔 로그에서 인증코드 확인 후 입력)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/sms/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "01012345678",
  "code": "123456"
}

###

# @name parentVerify  (verifySms 응답의 sms_token 사용)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/parent/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sms_token": "PASTE_SMS_TOKEN_HERE",
  "region": "서울",
  "school_code": "B100000393",
  "school_name": "테스트초등학교",
  "grade": 2,
  "school_type": "elementary"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 18 ── 캡처 업로드 (S3 미설정 시 skip_upload=true)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name capturePresign
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/capture/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{lurkerToken}}

###

# @name captureSubmit  (capturePresign 응답의 s3_key 사용)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/capture/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{lurkerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "s3_key": "PASTE_S3_KEY_FROM_PRESIGN_HERE",
  "school_code": "B100000393",
  "school_name": "테스트초등학교",
  "grade": 2,
  "class_num": 3
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 19 ── 관리자 API
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 19-1. 관리자 계정 생성 (최초 1회 — DB에 직접 superadmin 계정 seed 필요)
###       아래 명령으로 seed:
###       python -c "
###       import asyncio
###       from app.db import service_engine
###       from app.models.service_models import AdminUser, Base
###       from passlib.context import CryptContext
###       from sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import AsyncSession
###       from sqlalchemy.ext.asyncio import async_sessionmaker
###       pwd = CryptContext(schemes=['bcrypt']).hash('admin1234!')
###       async def seed():
###           async with service_engine.begin() as conn:
###               await conn.run_sync(Base.metadata.create_all)
###           Session = async_sessionmaker(service_engine)
###           async with Session() as s:
###               s.add(AdminUser(username='admin', hashed_password=pwd, role='superadmin'))
###               await s.commit()
###       asyncio.run(seed())
###       "

# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin1234!"
}

###

### 19-2. 아래 @adminToken 에 adminLogin 응답의 admin_token 붙여넣기

@adminToken = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

###

# @name listCaptures
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/captures
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

# @name approveCapture
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/captures/{{captureId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

# @name rejectCapture
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/captures/{{captureId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "첨부 이미지가 학급 알림장과 관련 없습니다."
}

###

# @name listReports
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/reports?status_filter=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

# @name suspendUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{user2Id}}/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "days": 7,
  "reason": "반복적인 욕설 사용"
}

###

# @name banUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{user2Id}}/ban
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "심각한 개인정보 유출"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Step 20 ── 게시글 삭제 (마지막에 실행)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# @name deletePost
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### 오류 케이스 확인 (각각 독립적으로 실행 가능)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# 401 — 인증 없이 접근
# @name unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?board_type=free

###

# 404 — 존재하지 않는 게시글
# @name notFound
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/99999999
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}

###

# 400 — 본문 너무 짧음 (5자 미만)
# @name validationError
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{memberToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "제",
  "content": "짧",
  "board_type": "free"
}

###

# 401 — 만료/잘못된 토큰
# @name invalidToken
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid.token.here

###
